Whole-Home Interior Renewal: St. Michael & Albertville, MN

We recently had the pleasure of transforming Sarah Peterson’s home in the St. Michael/Albertville area, providing a comprehensive color update across the living room, kitchen, hallway, and bedrooms. We replaced dated brown tones with a sophisticated, modern gray and traded a dark purple for a vibrant, bright blue that completely energized the living space. The bedroom received a fresh, custom color to create a calming retreat, and we finished the project by refreshing the bathroom ceiling to brighten the entire room from the top down. This full-scale interior renewal didn’t just change the look of the home; it improved the visual flow between rooms and significantly increased the property’s brightness and modern appeal.